        <Parent_String>television (telecommunication system) [300249920], telecommunication systems [300008610], infrastructural systems [300155846], systems by function [300242038], systems (equipment) [300008550], Object Groupings and Systems (hierarchy name) [300241489], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
